          "name": "Above the Avenue of Dreams",
          "description": "The roof of this building is covered with plants in glazed urns, with a few wooden chairs sitting in the center. From here you can see the Avenue of Dreams as it travels east and west. Climbing down would not be that hard. The city wall rises to the south, offering a more difficult route.",
