        "1309": {
          "vnum": 1309,
          "name": "On the Rooftops",
          "description": "You gain a whole other perspective of the city as you look out over the streets. It is easy to see them as streams and gullies, and the buildings as islands and stepping stones. To the west with a leap and a bound is Farath's Armory. The city wall rises to your south.",
