          "vnum": 1768,
          "name": "Above Jansens",
          "description": "Empty and filthy boxes lie scattered over this rooftop. Looking down you can see that you are over Jansen's Bargains. You see his sign as it sticks out from the doorway. Next to the door is a window, if you would care to visit.",
