        "1770": {
          "vnum": 1770,
          "name": "On the Rooftops",
          "description": "Looking down, you see that with very little effort, you could climb down into the palace garden and wander around. From this height, you can see that the flowers are arranged in a complex geometric pattern. Nearby buildings to the south allow you to go in that direction as well.",
