        "1308": {
          "vnum": 1308,
          "name": "City Wall",
          "description": "Several buildings nestle up against the wall. Like most of the dwellings in Mareldja, they have flat, solid stone roofs. Some look as if a climb down would not be too strenuous. To the east, the wall passes over the Gate of Air.",
