          "vnum": 1759,
          "name": "On the Rooftops",
          "description": "You gaze at the streets below from a distance of three stories. The building rests against the city wall, and you could probably climb up to the top if you tried. To the north over a narrow alley is another building and to the south is the roof of the Inn of the Golden Vanity.",
